snippet.title: subpar pool - launch trailer
snippet.description:
OUT NOW! BUY IT HERE: https://subparpool.com/#download

A whimsical adventure of playful pocket antics at the intersection of golf and pool, from the developer behind holedown, twofold inc. & rymdkapsel

subpar pool is a game by Martin Jonasson, with sound and music by Niklas Ström, art direction by Sonny Ross, and PR by Dana Trebella.
